#

Arugula Quinoa Bowl

25 min
$8.5
400 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

Dairy

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-Free

Cuisine:

Mediterranean

Course:

Main

Tags:

QuickHealthySaladBowl

Description

A refreshing and nutritious bowl packed with protein, greens, and a zesty dressing.

Ingredients

  • quinoa: 1 cup
  • arugula: 2 cups
  • cherry tomatoes: 1 cup
  • cucumber: 1
  • feta cheese: 1/2 cup
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • lemon juice: 1 tablespoon
  • salt: to taste
  • pepper: to taste
